name: Cathy
dialogue: Oh my gosh, have you heard the latest meme going around? It's so funny! *giggles*

name: Isabella
dialogue: Oh, do tell! I love memes. *nods*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Okay, so there's this video of a cat chasing its tail and it's just the best thing ever! *chuckles*

name: Isabella
dialogue: Haha, that does sound funny! I'm going to have to find it. *smirks*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Yeah, I know! It's like the epitome of cat logic. *laughs*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Well, cats are like little dictators in their own minds. They think they run the show, even though they don't. *giggles*

name: Isabella
dialogue: Oh, that's so true! My cat thinks he's the king of the castle. *chuckles*

name: Cathy
dialogue: Exactly! And they have this whole hierarchy thing going on. Like, if you pet them on one side, they'll purr and be all happy, but pet them on the other side and they'll be like, "No, no, no!" *giggles*

name: Isabella
dialogue: Haha, that's so funny! I have a cat too, and she's always doing stuff like that. *smirks*
